Whatever you're craving- salads, sandwiches, soup or even pasta...Sandwich House has you covered! Hearty slices of bread, generous on the meats and freshly made soups, SH will ensure your mouth is as happy as your tummy.  If you're in the mood for pasta, make sure you have a few extra minutes. While sandwiches come out within 5, I've seen them quote upwards of 20 minutes for pasta made to order.  When going to Sandwich House, I know I'm in for a good meal!

awesome sandwiches place! The bread is so fresh and flavorful and their combos are delicious.  The chicken sandwich is my fav! The soup/sandwich lunch special is a great deal- especially when they have the papa pomodoro soup.
